Text: Thank you so much! Really appreciate it.
Just to let you know this is 640x480p Fullscreen not widescreen.
@Cartoonworld we cap SD channels, and rather than doing 16:9 letterbox Nickelodeon does 4:3 AR. Alas, we can offer 4:3 640x480 as a result instead of the (slightly less common now) 624x352.
Didn't have a chance to watch this episode yesterday, thank you so much for the upload, that was really fast!
No complaints here. You posted this faster than anyone else and the video and sound quality were good. Thanks.
